Description: An automatic rule-based regression selection and regression averaging toolkit.
    You provide the data, 'ldt' calculates the benchmarks or does sensitivity 
    analysis. Currently, 'ldt' supports parameter estimation ('SUR'), binary classification ('logit'/'probit'),
    and time-series forecasting ('VARMA').
License: GPL (>= 3)
